msgid "Hi, I'm Zarifjon Baxtiyorov — a Backend Developer and Software Engineer from Tashkent, Uzbekistan. I specialize in building practical, scalable web applications using Python and Django."
msgstr "Men Zarifjon, Backend muhandisiman. Asosiy e'tiborimni Python/Django ekotizimida yuqori yuklamaga chidamli va foydalanuvchi ehtiyojlariga moslangan murakkab tizimlarni yaratishga qaratganman."

msgid "I'm passionate about automation, clean architecture, and solving real-world problems. I've worked on startup projects, contributed to academic research, and continue to grow in areas like Machine Learning and Deep Learning."
msgstr "Avtomatlashtirish, toza arxitektura va real muammolarni yechishga qiziqaman. Startup loyihalarida ishlaganman, akademik tadqiqotlarga hissa qo‘shganman va Machine Learning hamda Deep Learning sohalarida rivojlanishda davom etmoqdaman."

msgid "Currently finishing my Bachelor's degree in Software Engineering at Turin Polytechnic University in Tashkent (GPA 3.6/4). Open to freelance or full-time backend roles."
msgstr "Hozirda Toshkentdagi Turin Politexnika Universitetida Dasturiy Muhandislik bo‘yicha bakalavr diplomini yakunlamoqdaman (GPA 3.6/4). Frilanser yoki doimiy backend lavozimlariga ochiqman."

